At the policy level, we will, in discussion with the worksite management determine the need, methods and implementation of restricting tobacco use, increases physical activity, improving diet and enhancing access to treatments.

We would like to understand the policy level interventions in the entire worksite
a) What is the feasibility of peer-mentored interventions at the operational, research and policy levels to improve CVD health?
